Cindy Crawford, 56, drove her fans wild with a sultry new bikini snap on Instagram. In view of her 6.6million followers, the supermodel posed in a navy blue bikini with a white towelling shirt over the top. “Apres swim,” she captioned the snap. Linda Evangelista, who recently sued over a botched cosmetic procedure case and settled her case out of court, commented: “Yes,” with a love heart. Cindy’s daughter Kaia Gerber, whose father is Rande Gerber, wrote: “hot!” Melissa Obadash added: “Always flawless”.